Class PlayerDamage

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.se2019.server.model.PlayerDamage
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FinalFrenzyBeforeFirst, FinalFrenzyStandard, Healthy, SlightlyDamaged, VeryDamaged

    public abstract class PlayerDamage
extends Object
    This class implements a state pattern thanks to which it is possible to add new moves to a damaged player. See its subclasses: FinalFrenzyStandard, FinalFrenzyBeforeFirst, Healthy, SlightlyDamaged, VeryDamaged.
